# Project coding conventions for Cursor AI (Python data pipeline)

- Target Python 3.12; use `from __future__ import annotations` in all modules
- All functions must include type hints; prefer `pydantic.BaseModel` for data shapes
- Use `pathlib.Path` over raw string paths
- Log via the project logger in `src/etl/_logging.py`; never call `print()`
- New ETL stages must have a corresponding test in `tests/etl/`
